name: What happened with us? // Music Video
metadata:
{"name": "What happened with us? // Music Video 1/1", "description": "I created this Music NFT as a reminder of sunny days, of childhood, of carelessness and lightness. Do you remember those days when you were so free and happy and you didnb�t have any problems? I want you to stay in this lightness of mind all the time. Just listen to my song, look at the footage. I hope that I was able to convey to you the atmosphere of those times of freeness. 

I really want as many people as possible to be happy and understand that even in the most difficult of times, you can be happy and find beauty in the little things. Difficult times and problems  will always happen in our lives, I understand this perfectly. But, there are also good moments in our life. Just take a closer look around. So let's focus on the positive aspects. 

To everyone who viewed this video, to everyone who heard this song - I wish you to be happy!

I make all my songs and all my videos on my own. I want to improve the quality of my work, so everything I get from this sale, I will invest in my development, and first of all in new equipment.
